    {
      "kind": "markup",
      "language": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Accessing classes",
        "",
        "objc support is implemented in the \"system://objc\" module. Classes can be retrieved by name.<br>",
        "Either use",
        "* getClass(classname) method or",
        "* class._className_ property",
        "",
        "Classes expose constructor, className, superClass properties"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "language": "xsmixed",
      "source": [
        "import * as objc from \"system://objc\"",
        "",
        "const NSString = objc.class.NSString;",
        "const NSURL = objc.getClass(\"NSURL\");",
        "const NSValue = objc.class.NSValue;",
        "const Box = objc.class.Box;",
        "const Box2 = objc.getClass(\"Box2\");",
        "NSURL, NSString, NSString.className, Box, Box2"
      ]
    },
